item.title: By: Sekuru Mhofu
item.dc:creator: Sekuru Mhofu
item.description: Ichokwadi kuti mitemo yeipi neipi nzvimbo zvinoda kutevedwa. Ukaita chandagwinyira kuramba kurairwa inofa kwako. Panenge paine zvikonzero zvakaiswa kuti tsika dzichengetedzeke, saka iwe ukaita madiro ako unofuma woti dai ndakaziva. Ingave nyika, dunhu kuna mumba chaimo mune mitemo yamo. Hapana chaunobva nekutevedza mitemo yacho asi ukaita zano ndega unosiya jira mumasese. Handina kumbokura ndichiziva kuti Tsika dzedu dzine upfumi hweungwaru hwakadaro
